data.title: Hyeri Lee Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Hyeri Lee with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Was scouted at a talent show by Dream T Entertainment while she was in middle school

A member of Girl's Day, a South Korean girl group

In 2019, joined Creative Group ING after her contract with Dream T Entertainment ended

In 2019, became a member of UNICEF's Honors Club

Won Celebrity YouTuber of the Year at the 2020 Brand of the Year Awards
